quran[24]{c,v,t,f}:
  51,55,"Ṣèrántí nítorí pé, dájúdájú ìrántí máa wúlò fún àwọn onígbàgbọ́ òdodo."
  51,56,"Àti pé Èmi kò ṣẹ̀dá àlùjànnú àti ènìyàn bí kò ṣe pé kí wọ́n lè jọ́sìn fún Mi."
  51,57,"Èmi kò gbèrò arísìkí kan láti ọ̀dọ̀ wọn. Èmi kò sì gbèrò pé kí wọ́n máa bọ́ Mi."
  52,46,"Ọjọ́ tí ète wọn kò níí fi kiní kan rọ̀ wọ́n lọ́rọ̀. A kò sì níí ràn wọ́n lọ́wọ́."
  52,47,"Àti pé dájúdájú ìyà kan ń bẹ fún àwọn tó ṣàbòsí yàtọ̀ sí (ìyà ọ̀run) yẹn, ṣùgbọ́n ọ̀pọ̀lọ́pọ̀ wọn ni kò mọ̀."
  52,48,"Ṣe sùúrù fún ìdájọ́ Olúwa Rẹ, dájúdájú ìwọ wà ní ojútó Wa. Kí ó sì ṣe àfọ̀mọ́ pẹ̀lú ẹyìn fún Olúwa rẹ nígbà tí o bá fẹ́ dìde.1 {1}",1:[Nínú Sunan Abī Dāwud, láti ọ̀dọ̀ bàbá Barzah ’Azlamiy - kí Allāhu yọ́nú sí i -, ó sọ pé, Òjíṣẹ́ Allāhu - kí ìkẹ́ àti ọlà Allāhu máa bá a - máa ń sọ ní ìparí nígbà tí ó bá fẹ́ dìde kúrò lórí ìjókòó]
  53,40,"Àti pé dájúdájú iṣẹ́ rẹ̀, láìpẹ́ wọ́n máa fi hàn án."
  53,41,"Lẹ́yìn náà, wọ́n máa san án ní ẹ̀san rẹ̀, ní ẹ̀san tó kún jùlọ."
  53,42,"Àti pé dájúdájú ọ̀dọ̀ Olúwa rẹ ni òpin (ìrìn-àjò ẹ̀dá)."
  54,31,"Dájúdájú Àwa rán igbe kan ṣoṣo sí wọn. Wọ́n sì dà bí koríko gbígbẹ tí àgbẹ̀ dáná sun."
  54,32,"Dájúdájú A ṣe al-Ƙur’ān ní ìrọ̀rùn fún ṣíṣe ìrántí. Ǹjẹ́ olùrántí wà báyìí bí?"
  54,33,"Ìjọ Lūt pe àwọn ìkìlọ̀ ní irọ́."
  55,25,"Nítorí náà, èwo nínú àwọn ìdẹ̀ra Olúwa ẹ̀yin ènìyàn àti àlùjànnú ni ẹ máa pè ní irọ́?"
  55,26,"Gbogbo ẹni tó wà lórí ilẹ̀ máa tán."
  55,27,"Ojú Olúwa rẹ, Atóbi, Alápọ̀n-ọ́nlé sì máa wà títí láéláé."
  56,16,"Wọn yóò rọ̀gbọ̀kú sórí rẹ̀, wọn sì máa dojú kọra wọn."
  56,17,"Àwọn ọ̀dọ́kùnrin tí kò níí darúgbó yó sì máa lọ bọ̀ láààrin wọn"
  56,18,"pẹ̀lú àwọn ife omi, ohun ìrọmi fẹ̀ǹfẹ̀ àti ife ọtí aládùn láti inú odò kan tó ń ṣàn (káà kiri ọ̀dọ̀ wọn)."
  57,7,"Ẹ gbàgbọ́ nínú Allāhu àti Òjíṣẹ́ Rẹ̀. Kí ẹ sì ná nínú ohun tí Ó fi yín ṣe àrólé lórí rẹ̀. Nítorí náà, àwọn tó gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo nínú yín, tí wọ́n sì náwó (sí ojú ọ̀nà ẹ̀sìn), ẹ̀san tó tóbi wà fún wọn."
  57,8,"Kí ni ó mu yín tí ẹ̀yin kò fi níí gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo nínú Allāhu? Òjíṣẹ́ náà sì ń pè yín nítorí kí ẹ lè gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo nínú Olúwa yín. Allāhu sì ti gba àdéhùn lọ́wọ́ yín, tí ẹ̀yin bá jẹ́ onígbàgbọ́ òdodo."
  57,9,"Òun ni Ẹni tó ń sọ àwọn āyah tó yanjú kalẹ̀ fún ẹrúsìn Rẹ̀ nítorí kí ó lè mu yín kúrò nínú àwọn òkùnkùn wá sínú ìmọ́lẹ̀. Dájúdájú Allāhu ni Aláàánú, Àṣàkẹ́-ọ̀run fún yín."
  58,1,"Dájúdájú Allāhu ti gbọ́ ọ̀rọ̀ (obìnrin) tó ń bá ọ ṣe àríyànjiyàn nípa ọkọ rẹ̀, tí ó sì ń ṣàròyé fún Allāhu. Allāhu sì ń gbọ ìsọ̀rọ̀gbèsì ẹ̀yin méjèèjì. Dájúdájú Allāhu ni Olùgbọ́, Olùríran."
  58,2,"Àwọn tó ń fi ẹ̀yìn ìyàwó wọn wé ti ìyá wọn nínú yín, àwọn ìyàwó kì í ṣe ìyá wọn. Kò sí ẹni tí ó jẹ́ ìyá wọn bí kò ṣe ìyá tí ó bí wọn lọ́mọ.Dájúdájú wọ́n ń sọ aburú nínú ọ̀rọ̀ àti ọ̀rọ̀ irọ́. Dájúdájú Allāhu ni Alámòójúkúrò, Aláforíjìn. {1}",1:[Kíyè sí i, òfin tó ṣe é ní èèwọ̀ fún ọkọ láti fi ẹ̀yìn ìyàwó rẹ̀ wé ẹ̀yìn ìyá rẹ̀, òfin náà l’ó ṣe é ní èèwọ̀ fún un láti fi wé ẹ̀yìn ìyá tó fún un ní ọyàn mú ní kékeré nígbà tí kò tí ì já l’ẹ́nu ọyàn.]
  58,3,"Àwọn tó ń fi ẹ̀yìn ìyàwó wọn wé ti ìyá wọn, lẹ́yìn náà tí wọ́n ń ṣẹ́rí kúrò níbi ohun tí wọ́n sọ, wọn máa tú ẹrú kan sílẹ̀ lóko ẹrú ṣíwájú kí àwọn méjèèjì tó lè súnmọ́ ara wọn. Ìyẹn ni À ń fi ṣe wáàsí fún yín. Allāhu sì ni Alámọ̀tán nípa ohun tí ẹ̀ ń ṣe níṣẹ́."